# Backend Utilities Module

## PURPOSE
Helper functions and utilities used across backend.

## CONTAINS
- logger.js: Logging utility (Winston/Pino)
- emailValidator.js: Email validation helper
- tokenGenerator.js: JWT token generation
- errorFormatter.js: Error response formatter

## UTILITIES
- Log requests and errors
- Validate email formats
- Generate secure tokens
- Format consistent API responses
- Handle async errors

## REFERENCES
- Parent: /backend/.windsurf
- Root: /.windsurf
- Used by: /backend/routes/*, /backend/middleware/*

## RULES
- Keep utilities pure and testable
- No side effects in helper functions
- Proper error handling
- Document function parameters
